  "title": "Sales Promoter",
  "description": "<ol>\n  <li>Highlight key product features to effectively drive customer interest and boost sale</li>\n  <li>Understand customer needs and recommend the most appropriate product</li>\n  <li>Consistently achieve or surpass set sales targets</li>\n  <li>Maintain attractive and well-organised product displays</li>\n  <li>Monitor sales performance and regularly report results to management</li>\n  <li>Have basic computer skills and familiarity with Point Of Sale systems</li>\n  <li>Commission will be based on meeting sales target</li>\n  <li>Actively promote and demonstrate household appliances</li>\n  <li>Assist with general retail and store support duties</li>\n</ol>\n<p>We are seeking enthusiastic and self motivated Sales Promoter to join our sales team. If you have strong customer service skills and enjoy engaging with shoppers, this is an excellent opportunity to represent trusted household appliance brands.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Basic Salary + Attractive Commissions Package</p>",
